item.title: The Ultimate Search Engine Optimization (SEO) Quiz 2021
item.description: We all know that search engine optimization (SEO) is the art and science of getting pages to rank higher in search engines like Google, Bing, Duckduckgo etc. Since search is one of the main ways people discover online content, ranking higher in search engines can lead to an increase in website traffic. SEO has two key objectives. The first is to help you understand what online users are looking for - so that you can create high-quality content to serve their purpose.
